class  RMLInputParameters
 Class for the input parameters of the Online Trajectory Generation algorithm. More...

Detailed Description

Header file for the class RMLInputParameters.

The class RMLInputParameters constitutes the basis class for the actual interface classes RMLPositionInputParameters and RMLVelocityInputParameters, which are both derived from this one.
